verses.rendering:
"Behold, it is written before Me:
I will not keep silent;
I will repay — I will repay into their lap —"

Therefore this is what the Lord GOD says:
"Behold, My servants shall eat, but you shall be hungry;
My servants shall drink, but you shall be thirsty;
My servants shall rejoice, but you shall be put to shame."

"You shall leave your name as a curse-word for My chosen ones;
the Lord GOD will put you to death.
But His servants He will call by another name,"
